       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI10800.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI10800.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Lista Ausęncias                                            *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI10800         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD7601 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5303 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV1080.
       COPY COCV1081.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY ARCL0039.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY AQCW0005.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            SWITCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  SW-SWITCH.
           05 SW-CURSOR                  PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
              88 SW-CURSOR-NONE                    VALUE '0'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-1                       VALUE '1'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-2                       VALUE '2'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-3                       VALUE '3'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-4                       VALUE '3'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT7601 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT7601'.
           05 CON-COVT5303 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5303'.
           05 CON-SEP      PIC X(01) VALUE '-'.
           05 CON-S        PIC X(01) VALUE 'S'.
           05 CON-AP       PIC X(02) VALUE 'AP'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-DTMESANO.
              10 WS-ANO                 PIC  X(04)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 FILLER                 PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-MES                 PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 FILLER                 PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-DIA                 PIC  X(02)  VALUE '01'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI10800'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *              DECLARACOES DE CURSORES DB2                     *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 WS-CIDEMP-MIN             PIC  X(03) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CIDEMP-MAX             PIC  X(03) VALUE SPACES.

           05 WS-NIDPROJECTO-MIN        PIC  X(08) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NIDPROJECTO-MAX        PIC  X(08) VALUE SPACES.

           05 WS-DDATAUS-MIN            PIC  X(07) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DDATAUS-MIN.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MIN-ANO     PIC  X(04)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MIN-SEP     PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MIN-MES     PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.

           05 WS-DDATAUS-MAX            PIC  X(07) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DDATAUS-MAX.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MAX-ANO     PIC  X(04)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MAX-SEP     PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MAX-MES     PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.

           05 FILLER                    PIC  X(01) VALUE SPACES.

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT76 CURSOR FOR
                 SELECT
                        CIDEMP
                      , DDATAUS
                      , NIDPROJECTO
                      , NHORAS
                      , CSITU
                      , CUSERAPR
                      , DDATAPR
                   FROM COVT7601

                  WHERE ( CIDEMP      > :COCD7601-CIDEMP
                     OR ( CIDEMP      = :COCD7601-CIDEMP
                    AND   DDATAUS     > :COCD7601-DDATAUS )
                     OR ( CIDEMP      = :COCD7601-CIDEMP
                    AND   DDATAUS     = :COCD7601-DDATAUS
                    AND   NIDPROJECTO >= :COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO ) )

                    AND   CIDEMP   >= :WS-CIDEMP-MIN
                    AND   CIDEMP   <= :WS-CIDEMP-MAX
                    AND   SUBSTR(CHAR(DDATAUS), 1, 7)
                          >= :WS-DDATAUS-MIN
                    AND   SUBSTR(CHAR(DDATAUS), 1, 7)
                          <= :WS-DDATAUS-MAX

               ORDER BY CIDEMP
                      , DDATAUS
                      , NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI10800         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------

       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *    CALL 'ARREBENTA'.
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV1080-MSG.
           MOVE COCV1080-ASE               TO COCV1081-ASE.

           INITIALIZE WS-VARIAVEIS
                      COCV1081-ADE          REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                 ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV1080-ADE' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV1080-ADE  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)

              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1080-ADE                TO COCV1081-ADE.


           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2001-OBT-NTRAB
                 THRU 2001-OBT-NTRAB-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2010-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2103-VALIDACOES-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2020-OPEN
                 THRU 2029-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                 THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-OK
                    PERFORM 2040-CONTINUA
                       THRU 2049-CONTINUA-EXIT
                 ELSE
                    COMPUTE COCV1081-DIMINUI-LENGTH =
                            COCV1081-INDICE-INVERSO *
                            COCV1081-LENGTH-OCCUR
                    COMPUTE COCV1081-LENGTH =
                            COCV1081-LENGTH -
                            COCV1081-DIMINUI-LENGTH

                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV1081-CIDEMP-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-SEM-DADOS
                      TO COCV1081-CIDEMP-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV1081-CIDEMP-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF

              PERFORM 2070-CLOSE
                 THRU 2079-CLOSE-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2001-OBT-NTRAB.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2001-OBT-NTRAB.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2001-OBT-NTRAB' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I    TO COCD5303-CUTILIZA.

           EXEC SQL
             SELECT NTRABALHADOR
               INTO :COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
               FROM COVT5303_PESSOAS
            WHERE CUTILIZA = :COCD5303-CUTILIZA
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5303               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
             THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
                MOVE COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR TO COCV1080-CIDEMP
                MOVE COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR TO COCV1081-CIDEMP
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV1081-CANO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-CUTILIZA-NOTFND TO COCV1081-CANO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV1081-CANO-CAPLIC
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV1081-CANO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-CUTILIZA-NOTFND TO COCV1081-CANO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV1081-CANO-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2001-OBT-NTRAB-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2010-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2010-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2010-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF COCV1080-CANO NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE COCV1080-CANO             TO WS-DDATAUS-MIN-ANO
              MOVE COCV1080-CANO             TO WS-DDATAUS-MAX-ANO
           ELSE
              MOVE '0001'                    TO WS-DDATAUS-MIN-ANO
              MOVE '9999'                    TO WS-DDATAUS-MAX-ANO
           END-IF.

           IF COCV1080-CMES NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE COCV1080-CMES             TO WS-DDATAUS-MIN-MES
              MOVE COCV1080-CMES             TO WS-DDATAUS-MAX-MES
           ELSE
              MOVE '01'                      TO WS-DDATAUS-MIN-MES
              MOVE '12'                      TO WS-DDATAUS-MAX-MES
           END-IF.

           MOVE CON-SEP                      TO WS-DDATAUS-MIN-SEP.
           MOVE CON-SEP                      TO WS-DDATAUS-MAX-SEP.

           IF COCV1080-CIDEMP EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE SPACES                    TO WS-CIDEMP-MIN
              MOVE ALL '9'                   TO WS-CIDEMP-MAX
           ELSE
              MOVE COCV1080-CIDEMP           TO WS-CIDEMP-MIN
                                                WS-CIDEMP-MAX
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1080-CIDEMP-PAG        TO COCD7601-CIDEMP.
           MOVE COCV1080-NIDPROJECTO-PAG   TO COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCV1080-DDATAUS-PAG       TO COCD7601-DDATAUS.

       2103-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2020-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2020-OPEN.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               OPEN CURCOT76
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT7601               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2029-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2030-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-FETCH.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2030-FETCH' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              FETCH CURCOT76
              INTO
                  :COCD7601-CIDEMP
                , :COCD7601-DDATAUS
                , :COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO
                , :COCD7601-NHORAS
                , :COCD7601-CSITU
                , :COCD7601-CUSERAPR
                , :COCD7601-DDATAPR
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT7601               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2039-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2040-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2040-CONTINUA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2040-CONTINUA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROES                     TO COCV1081-INDICE.
           PERFORM 2050-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL DB2-NOTFND
                OR COCV1081-PAGINA-CHEIA
                OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT COCV1081-PAGINA-CHEIA
                    COMPUTE COCV1081-INDICE-INVERSO EQUAL
                         COCV1081-INDICE-INVERSO - COCV1081-INDICE
                    COMPUTE COCV1081-DIMINUI-LENGTH EQUAL
                         COCV1081-INDICE-INVERSO * COCV1081-LENGTH-OCCUR
                    COMPUTE COCV1081-LENGTH EQUAL COCV1081-LENGTH -
                         COCV1081-DIMINUI-LENGTH
                    SET  VIAL0002-FIM-CONSULTA TO TRUE
              END-IF
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                    SET  VIAL0002-FIM-CONSULTA TO TRUE
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2049-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2050-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-TRATA-OCCURS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-TRATA-OCCURS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Se seleccionado "Só ausęncias por aprovar"
      *--- e ausęncia já aprovada, despreza o registo

           IF  COCV1080-SONAOAPR = CON-S
           AND COCD7601-CSITU    = CON-AP
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               ADD 1 TO COCV1081-INDICE

               MOVE COCD7601-CIDEMP       TO COCV1081-D-CIDEMP
                                             (COCV1081-INDICE)
               MOVE COCD7601-DDATAUS      TO COCV1081-D-DDATAUS
                                             (COCV1081-INDICE)
               MOVE COCD7601-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV1081-D-NIDPROJECTO
                                             (COCV1081-INDICE)
               MOVE COCD7601-NHORAS       TO COCV1081-D-NHORAS
                                             (COCV1081-INDICE)
               MOVE COCD7601-CSITU        TO COCV1081-D-CSITU
                                             (COCV1081-INDICE)
               MOVE COCD7601-CUSERAPR     TO COCV1081-D-CUSERAPR
                                             (COCV1081-INDICE)
               MOVE COCD7601-DDATAPR      TO COCV1081-D-DDATAPR
                                             (COCV1081-INDICE)
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2030-FETCH
              THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT.

       2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2070-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2070-CLOSE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2070-CLOSE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               CLOSE CURCOT76
           END-EXEC.

       2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF COCV1080-NMAXLIST EQUAL ZEROES
              MOVE VIAL0001-CAPLIC         TO ARCL0039-CAPLIC
              MOVE VIAL0001-COPCAO         TO ARCL0039-COPCAO
              PERFORM ARCR0039-NMAXLIST
                 THRU ARCR0039-NMAXLIST-EXIT

              IF ETCL0002-ABEND-DB2
                 MOVE ETCL0002-TABLE-NAME  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME
                 MOVE ETCL0002-SQLCA       TO VIAL0002-SQLCA
              END-IF

              MOVE ARCL0039-NMAXLIST       TO COCV1081-NMAXLIST
           ELSE
              MOVE COCV1080-NMAXLIST       TO COCV1081-NMAXLIST
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1081-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV1081-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV1081-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE COCV1081-INDICE            TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCR0039 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
